00:59:42.476 --> 00:59:47.543
that.
Then take a gas from A

00:59:47.543 --> 00:59:56.810
to B to C to
D and back to A.

00:59:56.810 --> 00:59:57.710
That was the Carnot engine.

01:00:01.710 --> 01:00:05.887
So, let's see what we are doing.
In the process AB,

01:00:05.887 --> 01:00:08.619
